These rules define the way of organization and operation of the Course Center the way of
financing, as well as the selection and activity of the academic staff, for the provision of courses
aimed at professional, theoretical and practical knowledge in various fields The conditions that
must be fulfilled in order to obtain the license, respecting the provisions and the norms
established by the Albanian government The validity of the certificate issued at the end of the
completion of the course level accredited by the Ministry of Education The final assessment of
trainees in accredited professional education and training is based on exams. The criteria and
rules of the exams and tests are determined by the instruction of the ministry
